{
  "stem": "16790.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The body was mounted on a plank and it was tilted-- --and they had some prayers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was-- the body was covered by the Nazi flag.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was tilted on this board and then when the prayers were done-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --the body was in a bag and the bag was dropped into the ocean and then it just about immediately sank.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they must have had weights on it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then it was over and plunk, he was gone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they folded up the Nazi flag and pulled the plank in and that was it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I thought, gee, it seems kind of a strange way to end someone's life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I had heard they were going to have this funeral, so I was-- I wanted to see this thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't really that late at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't like-- it was like maybe 9:30, ten o'clock, I thought.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were invited to-- to come to-- to the service.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was announced over the PA system, if I recall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how I knew it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I mean, you couldn't read in those days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember wondering what this place was going to be like because my mother told me it was going to be warm.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this-- and the weather started to get quite warm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, it got hot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And once we got there, there was a tremendous amount of anticipation what was going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then they heard-- we heard that they weren't going to let us in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were already in the harbor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had gone into the harbor.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
